---
title: Herby Grilled Pork Chops with Grilled Greek Salad
description: Our fabulous Greek pesto loads tender pork chops with bold herby flavour! Big wedges of red onion and sweet bell pepper are easy to grill, then chop into bite-sized chunks for the salad!
